Package de.espirit.firstspirit.access.store

Enum IDProvider.UidType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<IDProvider.UidType>
      • de.espirit.firstspirit.access.store.IDProvider.UidType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<IDProvider.UidType>
    Enclosing interface:
    IDProvider
    public static enum IDProvider.UidType
extends Enum<IDProvider.UidType>
    Defines the name space in which the unique identifier has to be unique. Each IDProvider supporting uid's (IDProvider.hasUid()) provides a static field to the belonging UidType (e.g. PageFolder.UID_TYPE).

    See usages for existing uid type mappings.

    Since:
    4.0
    See Also:
    Store.getStoreElement(String, de.espirit.firstspirit.access.store.IDProvider.UidType)
